{"tid":1927326,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"朗尼炮轟英國應對疫情緩慢　華倫西亞有球員確診","createTime":"2020-03-15T17:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T17:08:50.000Z","uid":41309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2a90a554382d64faff57aa0a7e8a45c3236cb219","tid":1927326,"uid":41309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:08:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514607-20200315.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514607-20200315.htm&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BviiczFR88nQiTnqliI8U3YY%3D&h=c219ddaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514607-20200315.htm&h=c418180a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514607-20200315.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1514607_1_L_20200315223622.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1514607_1_L_20200315223622.jpg&h=969b86df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英格蘭足球代表隊前隊長朗尼，批評英國政府與足總應對新型肺炎疫情的手法緩慢，形容當局在疫情期間對球員好像「白老鼠」一樣。<br />\n<br />\n朗尼在《星期日泰晤士報》撰文，質疑為何當其他地區都叫停聯賽，英超賽會及英格蘭足總要等到阿仙奴領隊阿迪達確診，才宣布將聯賽推遲至下月。他又指，如果自己家人因而受到感染，「永不會原諒」當局。<br />\n<br />\n新型肺炎疫情在歐洲球壇進一步蔓延，西甲球會華倫西亞有5名職球員確診，包括阿根廷後衛加雷。球會聲明指，5人正在家中隔離，強調所有人情況良好。"}]}